1.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Stadium Street Parking
1.plot: Season 3 of Section420: Talkin' Yankees kicks off 2018 Spring Training with a quick update on the squad and helps fans find smart street parking around Yankee Stadium instead of wasting money on overpriced garages and lots.

2.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2018 Yankees Opening Day Weekend
2.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees reviews the news and notes surrounding the team as they officially jump out of the gate for the 2018 season and then head to the playground for some serious business.

3.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - It's Didi Time!!
3.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees sheds light the team's energetic sprout from a mediocre start to the 2018 season and praises the emergence of Didi Gregorious as a serious MVP-caliber shortstop.

4.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - All's Well in Yankeeland
4.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees discusses the 2018 debut of Greg Bird to a major league roster which has left little to complain about by the Memorial Day Weekend point of the season.

5.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Rotation Hanging in the Balance
5.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees takes the cat for a walk and discusses the front office options to add a competent Starting Pitcher to the Rotation.

6.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Judge's Chipped Wrist
6.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees has a full plate of talking' with the recent injuries to Aaron Judge and Gary Sanchez as well as a review on Cashman's moves to pick up J.A. Happ and Zach Britton in order to catch those surging Red Sox.

7.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Wild Card Destiny
7.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees faces the reality that the Yankees will have to take the Wild Card route into the Post Season and discusses how they will use September to get healthy.

8.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The Judge Returns
8.plot: Aaron Judge is back!!. Section420: Talkin' Yankees debates who should start the Do-or-Die Wild Card game and discusses if Gary Sanchez's bat is worth the defensive risk of being behind the plate.

9.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Bring on Boston!
9.plot: Section420:Talkin' Yankees gives a quick wrap-up on how the Yankees swatted the A's like a fly in the do-or-die Wild Card game and a Tale of the Tape for going up against the Boston Red Sox in the Divisional Round.

10.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - End of the Subway Line
10.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees analyzes the Yanks' elimination in the Divisional Series at the hands of the Boston Red Sox and after is joined by a Special Guest to discuss what Offseason choices lie ahead for GM Brian Cashman.

11.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The Old Yankee Stadium
11.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees explains the re-signings of CC Sabathia and Brett Gardner for 2019 and then gives a History Lesson about the Old Yankee Stadium.

12.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Holiday Shopping and Mo's Fame
12.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees helps ring in 2019 with the latest front office news and weighs in on Mariano Rivera and Andy Pettitte's odds of being voted into the Baseball Hall of Fame. Plus, take a trip down memory lane to the 1994 Yankees on the 25th Anniversary of the Strike Year.

13.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees: Hypothermia and The Dirty Dozen
13.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees battles the cold weather to check in on the frozen Manny Machado sweepstakes and lists the 12 Best All-Time Acquisitions by GM Brian Cashman.

14.title: 2019 February Spring Training Report
14.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees dishes out the latest Yankees News with Pitchers and Catchers close to reporting to Tampa for Spring Training and, in recognition of Black History Month, takes a look back at the distinguished baseball career of Elston Howard.

1.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2016 Season Preview of the New York Yankees
1.plot: New York Yankees fan James Zeiss rants about his favorite sports team in this humorous and informative web series.

2.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - A Terrible Start to the 2016 Season
2.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees reviews the Yanks disappointing start to the baseball season and explains what went wrong in April, outside of the cold weather.

3.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - MAY turned things Around
3.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees reviews how the team was able to get the season on track during the second month of the season what they need to fix in order to climb the ladder in the A.L. East.

4.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Sh%t or Get off the Pot
4.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees explains why the Yankees are likely to keep their productive veterans and make a push to become BUYERS come the Trading Deadline.

5.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Forever .500
5.plot: .500 continues to be a high water mark for the Yankees who have been plagued with inconsistent offense and faltering starting pitching from Nathan Eovaldi.

6.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2016 Subway Series Preview
6.plot: The Yankees and Mets limp into the 2016 Subway Series with the Trade Deadline looming and both teams desperate for wins , but there's no doubt Yankee Stadium is way better than CitiField.

7.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The Baby Bombers
7.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees drops by Arthur Avenue to discuss the youth movement GM Brian Cashman invoked on the roster and a postmortem on the rocky pinstripe tenure of Alex Rodriguez.

8.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The Wild Card Unicorns
8.plot: A Quickie (not that kind of quickie) Section420: Talkin' Yankees discusses the supernatural rise of Gary Sánchez and the Yanks improbable run to a Wild Card spot.

9.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - FALLing out of the Race
9.plot: The Yanks hit a reality check up in Fenway that knocks them out of the Wild Card race, and to make matters worse, they will honor the career of arch-nemesis David Ortiz during his final visit to Yankee Stadium.

1.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2017 New York Yankees Preview
1.plot: Season 2 of Section420: Talkin' Yankees Begins!. Get the team roster moves and updates you missed over the winter because you were too saturated with football.

2.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Gearing up for 2017 Opening Day
2.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees reviews the high and low points of Spring Training and complains about the stupid World Baseball Classic getting Didi Gregorius injured.

3.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Flowers are Blooming in April
3.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees discusses the team's rosy start to the 2017 Baseball season and why Aaron Judge is turning into Must-See-TV.

4.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The Fidget Spinner
4.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees explains how the Yanks continue to be the latest craze in baseball and what they need to do to overcome the Chapman stint to the DL.

5.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2017 Yankees are For Realz
5.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees believes the Yankees have proven themselves as the best team in the AL East and makes a case for Aaron Judge to participate in the Homerun Derby.

6.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - Trade Deadline Shopping Spree
6.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees reviews the blockbuster trade the Yankees made to pick up Todd Frazier, David Robertson, and Tommy Kahnle and explains why they should still be considered Postseason-bound.

7.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The Red Coats are Coming!
7.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees breaks down the final lap of the race against the pesky Boston Red Sox for the A. L. East crown.

8.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2017 Wild Card SHOWTIME
8.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees previews the 2017 New York Yankees upcoming One-Game showdown to keep their unlikely season alive.

9.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 2017 Playoff Party Ends
9.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees looks back and at the incredible playoff run that fell short of one game from reaching the 2017 World Series and analyzes the abrupt dismissal of Joe Girardi as Yankees Manager.

10.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - 'The Off-Season' Manager Search
10.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees opens "The Off-Season" with an update on the front office search for a sensitive manager, selects the All-Time Yankee Lineup, and states the case why Mike Mussina belongs in the Hall of Fame.

11.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - The 'Off-Season' Hoodie
11.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees reviews the front office decision to hire Aaron Boone as the new team manager and approves the surprise trade to bring reigning NL MVP Giancarlo Stanton to The Bronx. Plus, for added measure, take a trip down memory lane for the Top 10 Yankee Stadium Experiences.

12.title: Section420: Talkin' Yankees - "Who's the Worst" Yankee Tournament
12.plot: Section420: Talkin' Yankees takes a final lap towards Spring Training with a Sweet 16 Tournament to determine which Yankee Player in recent memory was "The Worst".
